        "code": "<!-- RC Sub-Collection Quick Links -->\n<section class=\"rc-ql\" aria-label=\"Quick links\">\n  <nav class=\"rc-ql__nav\">\n    <ul class=\"rc-ql__list\">\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-half-tights\">Golf Posters</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-split-shorts\">Golf Posters</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-golf posters\">Golf Posters</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-shirts\">Golf Shirts</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/lifestyle-clothing\">Graphic Shirts</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/lifestyle-clothing\">Hoodies</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-posters\">Posters</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-stickers\">Stickers</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </nav>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n.rc-ql {\n  background: #fbfbfb;\n  border-top: 1px solid #e9e9e9;\n  padding: 20px 0;\n}\n.rc-ql__nav {\n  max-width: 3000px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 0 5vw;\n}\n.rc-ql__list {\n  list-style: none;\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: nowrap;\n  gap: 14px;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n  overflow: auto;\n  scrollbar-width: none;\n}\n.rc-ql__list::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n.rc-ql__list a {\n  display: inline-block;\n  min-width: 140px;\n  padding: 9px 22px;\n  border: 1px solid #ddd;\n  border-radius: 3px;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  text-align: center;\n  font-style: var(--BTN-FONT-STYLE);\n  font-weight: 500;\n  font-family: var(--BTN-FONT-STACK);\n  font-size: 12px;\n  letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  color: #111;\n  background: #fbfbfb;\n  transition: background-color .2s ease-in-out, color .2s ease-in-out, border-color .2s ease-in-out;\n  white-space: nowrap;\n}\n.rc-ql__list a:hover,\n.rc-ql__list a:active {\n  background: #2A4D1F;\n  color: #fbfbfb;\n  border-color: #2A4D1F;\n}\n.rc-ql__list a:focus-visible {\n  outline: 2px solid #2A4D1F;\n  outline-offset: 2px;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 763px) {\n  .rc-ql__nav { padding: 0 10px; }\n  .rc-ql__list {\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: stretch;\n    gap: 10px;\n    overflow: visible;\n  }\n  .rc-ql__list a {\n    width: 100%;\n    min-width: 0;\n  }\n}\n</style>",
